<name>MAINTENANCE</name>
<section id="1001X_S0001" variety="S0001">
<name>MAINTENANCE</name>
<ttl id="1001X_S0001_731CO_T00FF" variety="T00FF">
<name>BRAKE</name>
<para id="RM000001AQU007X" category="N" type-id="3011J" name-id="MA02R-04" from="200601">
<name>GENERAL MAINTENANCE</name>
<subpara id="RM000001AQU007X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQJ00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT BRAKE LINE PIPES AND HOSES</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<ptxt>Work in a well-lighted area. Turn the front wheels fully to the right or left before beginning the inspection.</ptxt>
</atten4>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="P009958E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a mirror, check the entire circumference and length of the brake lines and hoses for:</ptxt>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Damage</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Wear</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Deformation</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Cracks</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Corrosion</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Leaks</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Bends</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Twists</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check all the clamps for tightness and the connections for leakage.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the hoses and lines are not near sharp edges, moving parts or the exhaust system.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the lines are installed properly and pass through the center of the grommets.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0008" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQO00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT BRAKE PEDAL</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>(See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000QSF006X"/>)</ptxt>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0009" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQP00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT PARKING BRAKE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>(See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UVR007X"/>)</ptxt>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0004" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQK00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT BRAKE LININGS</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the brake linings. Also check the brake linings of parking brake.  </ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0005" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQL00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT FRONT BRAKE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the front brake pads and discs (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000022JN000X"/>).</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0006" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQM00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT REAR BRAKE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the rear brake pads, discs linings and drums (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000025RN000X"/>).</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001AQU007X_01_0007" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AQN00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT OR CHANGE BRAKE FLUID</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>(See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000SRG004X"/>)</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Fluid</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>SAE J1703 or FMVSS No. 116 DOT3</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
